PN,31201
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1774519535
OL,3,CRugby Captain Maro Itoje on sport,
OL,4,Ceducation and the Nigerian state
OL,5,Cbanquet
OL,7,FEngland and British & Irish Lions
OL,8,Fcaptain Maro Itoje is balancing two
OL,9,Fdefining missions: building a legacy
OL,10,Fthrough education and leading England
OL,11,Ftowards what he believes could be a
OL,12,FWorld Cup triumph in 2027.
OL,14,F"I believe we can go to Australia in
OL,15,F2027 and win," he told me, with a
OL,16,Fconfidence he insists hasn't been
OL,17,Frocked by his side's disastrous Six
OL,18,FNations campaign.
OL,26,@vD@AOUwD@NO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1774519535
OL,3,CRugby Captain Maro Itoje on sport,
OL,4,Ceducation and the Nigerian state
OL,5,Cbanquet
OL,7,FIn his first interview since the
OL,8,Ftournament in which England lost four
OL,9,Fof their five matches, Itoje said how
OL,10,Fhe felt about the squad before and
OL,11,Fafter the campaign hasn't changed.
OL,13,FEngland's recent Six Nations campaign
OL,14,Ffell short of expectations, raising
OL,15,Fquestions about the team's direction
OL,16,Funder head coach Steve Borthwick.
OL,18,FBut Itoje remains resolute.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1774519535
OL,3,CRugby Captain Maro Itoje on sport,
OL,4,Ceducation and the Nigerian state
OL,5,Cbanquet
OL,7,F"I believe that this is a team that
OL,8,Fcan go out there and achieve amazing
OL,9,Fthings," he said.
OL,11,F"We have the coaches; we have the
OL,12,Fsquad, we have the personnel to do it."
OL,14,FRather than seeing failure, he sees
OL,15,Fdevelopment.
OL,17,F"In good time, we'll look at this
OL,18,Fperiod and say we learned crucial
OL,19,Flessons... which are going to put us
OL,20,Fin good stead for the future."
OL,26,@oD@AOUqD@HO]sD@AOUtD@gO]yD@AOU|D@^O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1774519535
OL,3,CRugby Captain Maro Itoje on sport,
OL,4,Ceducation and the Nigerian state
OL,5,Cbanquet
OL,7,FHe acknowledged England must improve
OL,8,Ftheir execution and accuracy, adding
OL,9,Fthat while there were signs of
OL,10,Fprogress against France, "there's
OL,11,Fstill another level to go".
OL,13,FItoje also offered a firm defence of
OL,14,FBorthwick.
OL,16,F"Steve is a fantastic coach... often
OL,17,Fthe coach gets the blame, but the
OL,18,Fcoach doesn't play the game. It's us
OL,19,Fas players."
OL,26,@rD@ZOUsD@ZO]xD@AOU{D@LO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1774519535
OL,3,CRugby Captain Maro Itoje on sport,
OL,4,Ceducation and the Nigerian state
OL,5,Cbanquet
OL,7,FHe was speaking to me on a visit to
OL,8,Ftwo London schools where pupils are
OL,9,Fbenefiting from extra tutoring thanks
OL,10,Fto his philanthropic project.
OL,12,FThe Maro Itoje Pearl Fund aims to
OL,13,Fsupport children from disadvantaged
OL,14,Fcommunities through sustained
OL,15,Finvestment in education.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1774519535
OL,3,CRugby Captain Maro Itoje on sport,
OL,4,Ceducation and the Nigerian state
OL,5,Cbanquet
OL,7,FNow 30 children from St Paul's Way
OL,8,FTrust Primary School and The Clara
OL,9,FGrant Primary School are the first in
OL,10,Fthe UK to benefit from the fund,
OL,11,Fthrough a partnership with Action
OL,12,FTutoring.
OL,14,FThe schools are both in the borough of
OL,15,FTower Hamlets, a deliberate choice
OL,16,Freflecting both need and urgency.
OL,18,FItoje pointed to the economic
OL,19,Frealities facing many families in the
OL,20,Farea.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1774519535
OL,3,CRugby Captain Maro Itoje on sport,
OL,4,Ceducation and the Nigerian state
OL,5,Cbanquet
OL,7,F"It's certainly timely," he said.
OL,9,F"The kids that we help, a majority of
OL,10,Ftheir families are on free school
OL,11,Fmeals, pupil premium.
OL,13,F"I don't have the precise figure to
OL,14,Fhand, but to qualify for that, you
OL,15,Fhave to have a family income of around
OL,16,F#12,500. And in London, that really
OL,17,Fdoesn't get you too far."
OL,19,FLaunched in Nigeria in 2023, the
OL,20,Fproject reflects Itoje's belief in the
OL,21,Ftransformative power of education.
OL,26,@oD@AOUyD@YO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1774519535
OL,3,CRugby Captain Maro Itoje on sport,
OL,4,Ceducation and the Nigerian state
OL,5,Cbanquet
OL,7,F"I guess education has always been
OL,8,Fsomething that's been drilled into me
OL,9,Ffrom my family, from my parents," he
OL,10,Fsaid.
OL,12,F"And any Nigerian British individual
OL,13,Fwill tell you the importance that
OL,14,Ftheir parents would have placed on
OL,15,Feducation.
OL,26,@oD@AOUqD@aO]tD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31209
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1774519535
OL,3,CRugby Captain Maro Itoje on sport,
OL,4,Ceducation and the Nigerian state
OL,5,Cbanquet
OL,7,F"The kids that we're in touch with
OL,8,Fnow, they're extremely disadvantaged,
OL,9,Fbut through education, they can
OL,10,Fcontrol their life... they can be
OL,11,Fwhatever they want to be... they can
OL,12,Fbuild a better life for themselves."
OL,14,FHis recent attendance at the Nigerian
OL,15,Fstate banquet at Windsor Castle,
OL,16,Fhosted by King Charles, was an
OL,17,Fopportunity to celebrate his dual
OL,18,Fidentity, British and Nigerian.
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@dO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31210
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1774519535
OL,3,CRugby Captain Maro Itoje on sport,
OL,4,Ceducation and the Nigerian state
OL,5,Cbanquet
OL,7,F"It was two countries which are very
OL,8,Fclose to my heart... I felt like I was
OL,9,Fin a movie," he said.
OL,11,FHe was sat next to Prime Minister Sir
OL,12,FKeir Starmer and described the
OL,13,Fconversation as "wide-ranging,"
OL,14,Fcovering politics, media, and the
OL,15,Fgoals of Nigeria's state visit.
OL,17,FThe pair also shared their experiences
OL,18,Fof leadership under pressure.
OL,26,@oD@AOUqD@LO]uD@QOUuD@_O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31211
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1774519535
OL,3,CRugby Captain Maro Itoje on sport,
OL,4,Ceducation and the Nigerian state
OL,5,Cbanquet
OL,7,F"We both shared our own perspective of
OL,8,Fhow we deal with media, and I guess
OL,9,Fpressure in our various worlds," he
OL,10,Fsaid, noting the weight of political
OL,11,Fdecision-making.
OL,13,F"There's probably a bit more life-
OL,14,Faltering consequence on his decisions."
OL,16,FI was curious to know whether the
OL,17,Fpolitics graduate saw himself stepping
OL,18,Finto the political arena post-rugby.
OL,26,@oD@AOUqD@`O]uD@AOUvD@gO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31212
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1774519535
OL,3,CRugby Captain Maro Itoje on sport,
OL,4,Ceducation and the Nigerian state
OL,5,Cbanquet
OL,7,F"I don't know. I don't know yet. I
OL,8,Fguess the time to make that decision
OL,9,Fis a little bit in the future," he
OL,10,Fsaid.
OL,12,F"But I'm definitely engaged in
OL,13,Fpolitics, I'm definitely interested in
OL,14,Fpolitics, and... despite a lot of
OL,15,Fcriticism politicians do get, I
OL,16,Fdefinitely think they do a lot of work
OL,17,Fthat we need as a country.
OL,26,@oD@AOUqD@_O]tD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31213
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1774519535
OL,3,CRugby Captain Maro Itoje on sport,
OL,4,Ceducation and the Nigerian state
OL,5,Cbanquet
OL,7,F"Obviously we always want more, we
OL,8,Falways want it to be better, we always
OL,9,Fwant it to be improved. But they do
OL,10,Fplay an important role."
OL,12,FWhether discussing England's World Cup
OL,13,Fambitions or the long-term goals of
OL,14,Fthe Pearl Fund, Itoje's outlook is
OL,15,Fshaped by collaboration,
OL,16,Fresponsibility, and belief.
OL,18,FOn the pitch, that belief is fixed
OL,19,Ffirmly on Australia in 2027.
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@XO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31214
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1774519535
OL,3,CRugby Captain Maro Itoje on sport,
OL,4,Ceducation and the Nigerian state
OL,5,Cbanquet
OL,7,FOff it, it is focused on expanding
OL,8,Feducational opportunities from Lagos
OL,9,Fto London.
OL,11,FIn both arenas, the goal is the same:
OL,12,Fto build something that lasts.
OL,14,FAnd if a career in politics is to
OL,15,Ffollow, there are children in Tower
OL,16,FHamlets who may just get behind him,
OL,17,Fonce they're old enough to vote.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
